QuestData.Title: Your Next Move
QuestData.Description:
Princess Talanji plans to travel north to Nazmir. The blood trolls there are a threat she believes her father refuses to acknowledge.
General Jakra'zet detests the Horde and cannot be trusted. As long as he remains in power, the city will never be safe.
You will also need to win over King Rastakhan here in Zuldazar. This city is vast and has many secrets.
QuestData.LogDescription: Choose your next move in Zandalar.
